I know this is probably the most random thing ever, but I fear that if I dont write down my plan somewhere I'll always check, then I may forget it and never be able to achieve it. 

So, this is my plan...

Stage 1: Take the very realistic fake handgun from my brothers room
Stage 2: Take it into a public place, i.e. school or town centre.
Stage 3: Make it really obvious I have a gun, maybe point it at a few ppl I'd love to see dead.
Stage 4: Keep repeating stage 3 until someone calls the police.
Stage 5: Wait for armed police to come and possition themselves everywhere around me with loaded guns
(And this is where you might what to look away)
Stage 6: Keep repeating stage 3, making threats ect ect until one of the armed police loses control and shoots me.
They're trained to shoot to kill. Plan is a success. I dont commit suicide but die and dont go into the 6th level of hell and become nothing but words.

Uh... Yeah.. Anyway, I'm still working on a few HP fics, so I'll post them once I'm done.

Hello! Calli here, and this is my first entry on here, as you can probably tell. Basically, this is my new livejournal account and I'm probbaly going to join some of the Harry Potter communities, and maybe some of the RP ones too.
